Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比昂与“玫瑰人生”接舷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为取得新的GUNDAM3号机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那里等待着的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中门少佐所率的警务部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对焦急的浦木一行人不屑一顾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉兹点燃了殖民地的推进燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎向地球的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒下的露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的死迫使妮娜与宿命对决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在浦木为阻止殖民地坠往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以GUNDAM3号机迎向决战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}强袭、阻止界限点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙世纪0083
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11月12日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以将殖民地坠往地球为目的的星尘作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可说正渐入佳境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷11时方向有1敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球轨道舰队还不可能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说有这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去通信室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是阿克西斯舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我舰队就在后方观战了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善后的事就有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以阿克西斯的名誉起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能做到这地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔日需要ZION一半舰艇的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如今只以这么点舰队进行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,块头大了点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地大约在月球与地球中间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试作GUNDAM3号机已经接触
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中立的阿克西斯舰队则退往后方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸取了一年战争的教训
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是敌人，却是次漂亮的殖民地坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是GUNDAM3号机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅凭他一架…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距坠落地球还剩14小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜败只在9小时内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就越过阻止界限点了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止界限点？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里被突破的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法阻止殖民地那样的质量了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前必须夺取殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并掉转它的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地的推进燃料还有剩余吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为坠往贾布罗而进行最终调整
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的第3轨道舰队在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阻止界限点前方的3-0-2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为迎击正在集结
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶不及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已无话可说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Field！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}I-Field：米诺夫斯基粒子中电磁波流动产生的磁场\N拥有使光束武器偏向的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距殖民地10万7千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距阻止界限点8小时22分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请许可MS出动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在3号机打开突破口之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉的体力真的能撑住吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会扯上这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在应酬ZION的亡灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从遇上GUNDAM之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束都被这样弹开的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那以光束为主的机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是阿尔比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请归舰补给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请归舰一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差少许就突破第一线了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人无法夺取殖民地的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的问题是敌人何时会在正面出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的地球轨道舰队大半是萨拉米斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没料到会被刺中软弱的肋腹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎预料之事经常会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎预料之事经常会发生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是第72战队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率先出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队将再次展开追击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使追不上敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后处理也请交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您刚才说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始武器柜的交换作业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速航行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩拉，我开Stamen出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Stamen：“雄蕊”的意思，与武器库系统(Orchis)\N合体后便成为RX-78 GP-03D 石斛兰(Dendrobium)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在战斗状态吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提、提督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严密的包围会使敌人背水一战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督，您在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，您想利用这状况做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽快让地球轨道舰队全面…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾米托夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止奇怪的策划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何GUNDAM3号机会交给了阿尔比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能依靠希玛舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要亲手去干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那样少佐您的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉多尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那架GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何曾怀着如此激动的心望着地球呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在正面的敌人出现之前打倒GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，距时限还剩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩3小时11分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已没有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也不会有援军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·巴普尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准许使用小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你立刻离开本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想以自己的意志看到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军方可不会发薪水给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一战速5分钟之后最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希玛的舰队太过超前了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们别无退路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希玛大人，前方有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去啊，卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能扩大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球轨道舰队…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，那排列状是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是交叉队形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船不后退？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至界限点的距离！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1万2百
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩21分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要过了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些罗嗦的的家伙也会闭嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是要将我与舰队做饵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向联邦摇尾乞怜？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让殖民地坠落？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是不坠落？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老家伙闭嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人突破一线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手不够用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷MS弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙，时间呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有4分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉没吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去殖民地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Field被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩50秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越过阻止界限点了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠往地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让它掉在贾布罗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1轨道舰队来电
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是迪拉兹舰队停止战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中止？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是G21
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系统Ⅱ的上部展开完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左翼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W11
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请增援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战有误差
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快展开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有防止殖民地坠落的秘诀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要加点热就会“砰”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样也算ZION的将领吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这么活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那些厚着脸皮踞坐在SIDE3的家伙颐指气使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有理由我就会背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想引导没有志向的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我本身的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被引导到阿克西斯那种边境之日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是生意倒闭之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希玛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这狮子身上的害虫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动哦，卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败军之将要好好认命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.77,0:23:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想伤了送给联邦的土特产哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.50,0:24:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯彻意志
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.80,0:24:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今殖民地还在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.02,0:24:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.92,0:24:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.06,0:24:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.10,0:24:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏过我的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.05,0:24:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.28,0:24:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我在宇宙中枭首示众吗？卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系统在瞄准着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.20,0:24:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别、别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.70,0:24:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZION万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.45,0:27:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预    告
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.64,0:27:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛的宇宙覆满阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.59,0:27:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的时代露出面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.54,0:27:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于殖民地要席卷地球了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.33,0:27:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在这之中恩怨的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.23,0:27:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今，浦木在战斗的尽头见到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.13,0:27:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时代的变迁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.05,0:27:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0083的帷幕即将拉上…
